Ayo.

308
00:19:27,481 --> 00:19:28,481
Sekretaris.

309
00:19:28,751 --> 00:19:29,912
Baik, Pak.

310
00:19:37,721 --> 00:19:41,392
Bagaimana aku bisa
bicara dengan gadis remaja?

311
00:19:41,461 --> 00:19:42,461
Coba kulihat.

